UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2027
1 A RESOLUTION honoring Dr. Samantha Shaver for her service as the current
2 president of the Kentucky Dental Association.
3 WHEREAS, Dr. Shaver has more than three decades of service to organized
4 dentistry in Kentucky with leadership advancing oral health policy at the local, state, and
5 national levels; and
6 WHEREAS, Dr. Shaver has a longstanding commitment to mentorship,
7 professional ethics, and public service, including advocacy for patients, dentists, and
8 access to quality oral healthcare; and
9 WHEREAS, Dr. Shaver obtained a bachelor degree from Kentucky Wesleyan
10 College and a doctor of medicine in dentistry from the University of Louisville School of
11 Dentistry; and
12 WHEREAS, Dr. Shaver is a fellow at the Academy of General Dentistry, the
13 International College of Dentists, the American College of Dentists, and the Pierre
14 Fauchard Academy; and
15 WHEREAS, Dr. Shaver is a current delegate of the American Dental Association,
16 president of the Kentucky Dental Association, and program coordinator of the Kentucky
17 Association of Women Dentists; and
18 WHEREAS, Dr. Shaver is a past president of the Louisville Dental Society and the
19 Kentucky Academy of General Dentistry, as well as a past trustee and regional director of
20 the Academy of General Dentistry;
21 NOW, THEREFORE,
22 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
23 Kentucky:
24 Section 1. The members of the Senate join Senator Julie Raque Adams in
25 honoring Dr. Samantha Shaver for her accomplished career and thanking her for her
26 service as the current president of the Kentucky Dental Association.
27 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall transmit a copy of this Resolution to
